e=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 就中電控告差餉物業估價署令其多交差餉一案，法官裁定差餉物業估價署勝訴，並要求中電須就青山發電廠、龍鼓灘發電廠及竹篙灣發電廠的主要設備用地繳交差餉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00002/1489773330803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00002%2F1489773330803&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=40544ec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00002%2F1489773330803&h=8779f919\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00002/1489773330803</a> (明報)"},{"pid":"908bf741e2fc786a1804d8f6d364cb61209c15f3","tid":160620,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:26:43.000Z","msg":"兩岸:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 國務院副總理汪洋抵達菲律賓首都馬尼拉展開4日訪問行程，中國政府表示將向菲律賓提供價值5億5000萬元人民幣的援助，用於建設橋樑和一個戒毒項目。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170318%2F00178_017.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c75a26ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_017.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 有韓媒報道指中國從本月15日開始全面封殺南韓旅遊產品，在中國經營的多家郵輪公司宣佈由即日起至6月底期間不再停泊南韓港口。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566717&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566717%26target%3D2&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=197ab59c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566717%26target%3D2&h=9509cf3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566717&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 遼寧錦州市公安分局局長王俊仁因受賄罪被法院判處15年有期徒刑，並罰款90萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_013.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170318%2F00178_013.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c1cc8076\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_013.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 廣東肇慶四會市政府稱將選址四會東城街道興建肇慶工業廢棄物處置中心，每年將處理近十萬噸廢物，大批民眾在市內聚集抗議，最終演變成警民衝突。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566720&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566720%26target%3D2&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8d8a9337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566720%26target%3D2&h=941becbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566720&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 潮州公安搗破一個非法買賣、持有槍支彈藥的犯罪集團，拘捕4名疑犯，並繳獲多支槍械及子彈等槍支配件。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00013/1489773359960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00013%2F1489773359960&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=fdda62ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00013%2F1489773359960&h=ba970a1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00013/1489773359960</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 台灣國民黨在自行清查舊有黨產時意外發現其尚有1947年向當時國民政府購買的美國黃金債券，按現在的黃金價計算，其價值超過385億新台幣。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170318%2F00178_020.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a526af9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00178_020.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566732&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566732%26target%3D2&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=714889e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566732%26target%3D2&h=6948b883\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566732&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)"},{"pid":"580ad9817eaa1d07b06659287279aa806c2b71e3","tid":160620,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:26:54.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 德國總理默克爾到訪白宮與美國總統特朗普會面，此行隨團者包括電子巨擘西門子、跨國高級汽車寶馬及工業零件生產商舍弗勒（Schaeffler）等企業的高層。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773364546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773364546&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c4abdcb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773364546&h=9c88aa9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773364546</a> (明報) <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170318/19962081?_ga=1.168057057.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170318%2F19962081%3F_ga%3D1.168057057.1316658954.1419942048&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e88767d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170318%2F19962081%3F_ga%3D1.168057057.1316658954.1419942048&h=3d0622f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170318/19962081?_ga=1.168057057.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 美國國務卿蒂勒森到訪南韓，其表示美國對朝鮮採取的「戰略忍耐」已經結束，揚言若朝鮮的核武威脅進一步增加，對朝鮮動武將是美方行動的選項之一。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773367370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773367370&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6dfb39b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773367370&h=19f27613\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773367370</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00180_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170318%2F00180_001.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e2382acd\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00180_001.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566744&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566744%26target%3D2&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d13eb15d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566744%26target%3D2&h=ac60cd9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566744&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 繼南韓前總統朴槿惠閨密崔順實的20歲女兒鄭柔娜年初在丹麥被捕後，丹麥檢方宣佈決定將她遣送回南韓。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773369834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773369834&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=75719196\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170318%2Fs00014%2F1489773369834&h=59e8cc1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170318/s00014/1489773369834</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566750&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566750%26target%3D2&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=481f8ca1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1566750%26target%3D2&h=f1d6467e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1566750&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 負責調查南韓前總統朴槿惠密友干政醜聞的獨立檢察組正式對涉案的國內第三大企業SK集團展開調查，檢方懷疑3名現任及前任高層曾賄賂朴槿惠，以換取其會長獲特赦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00180_022.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170318%2F00180_022.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a4d1b637\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170318/00180_022.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 日本法院宣判日本政府須為2011年福島核災負責，勒令政府和負責營運福島核電站的東京電力支付3855萬日圓賠償。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/ar